item.title: CVE-2023-40345|2024-10-08T18:28:25.965Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20delphix%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Delphix Plugin 3.0.2 and earlier does not set the appropriate context for credentials lookup, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to access and capture credentials they are not entitled to.

item.title: CVE-2023-40344|2024-10-08T18:29:42.817Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20delphix%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Delphix Plugin 3.0.2 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.
